		The Swiss 20 Franc Vreneli gold coin is one of the world's classic gold coins.  Neutral since its creation by the Congress of Vienna in 1815, Switzerland has long been synonymous with stability and fiscal strength due to its practice of backing its currency with large quantities of gold
		







