		Among the most popular gold coins in the world, British Sovereigns, or 'Kings,' in Brilliant Uncirculated (BU) condition are an outstanding way to invest in bulk gold. Our hand-selected George V sovereigns offer all the benefits of gold bullion plus complete financial privacy and the added profit potential of collectible coins--all for little additional cost.  These coins are a super value. 
		






 
 
 




