See a problem?
Let us know!


  
  
            Founded in 1965, A-Mark Precious Metals is a full-service precious metals trading company. Its products include gold, silver, platinum and palladium for storage and delivery in the form of coins, bars, wafers and grain. The company s services include financing, leasing, consignment, hedging and a variety of customized financial programs. A-Mark is an official distributor for many government mints throughout the world, including the United States Mint, the Royal Canadian Mint, the South African Mint and the Australian Mint. A-Mark s clients include coin and metal dealers, investors, collectors, mines, manufacturers, refiners, jewelers, investment advisors, merchants, commodity brokerage houses and central banks.
          






















