Buy & Sell Silver Coins in Phoenix and Scottsdale, AZ
American Precious Metals, Inc. is a retail and wholesale buyer and seller of gold, silver and platinum coins and bars. While we deal mainly in bullion products, we also handle numismatic coins.  We have performed countless estate valuations and appraisals for clients. We also have extensive experience helping investors set up Precious Metals IRAs.
APM is operated by a team of friendly, knowledgeable staff who will dedicate time and attention to ensure our customer’s needs are met. If you live in the Phoenix area, please stop by our office located at 2850 E. Camelback Road, Suite 185, just east of the Biltmore.
    








 

